articles.title: Oxford Blackbird Leys application for hundreds of new homes - Oxford Mail
articles.description: A developer in partnership with Oxford City Council has submitted a plan to build hundreds of new homes in Blackbird Leys.
articles.content:
The planning application made by Catalyst contains plans for 294 new rented and shared ownership homes across two sites, the district centre and Knights Road.
